Gets homolog associations for a gene.

bioentity_gene_homology_associations.Rd

The monarch_api class is included in return mainly for debugging.

bioentity_gene_homology_associations(gene)

Arguments

gene

A valid monarch initiative gene id.

Value

A list of (tibble of homolog information, monarch_api S3 class).

Details

https://api.monarchinitiative.org/api/bioentity/gene/NCBIGene

Examples

gene <-"NCBIGene:8314"
bioentity_gene_homology_associations(gene)
